snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin': Hotline 024 (The Medley Update) - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Thumbnail art by https://twitter.com/lavaprx !

And please, read this:

Our current release date is the one shown in the trailer, the mod is ready and we're currently in a testing state, bugs might appear and these have to be fixed, if we can't release it on time I'll tweet about it, but hopefully we'll deliver on time!

We would appreciate your comprehension!
